! Word

: anxiety [n]:
:: 不安
: extemporaneously [adv]:
:: 即興的に 準備なしに
: persuasive [adj]:
:: 説得力のある
: dispose [v]:
:: 処分する
:: to get rid of something
: disposal [n]:
:: 処分
: thereby [adv]:
:: それにより
: disruption [n]:
:: 分断 分裂 途絶



: get started [v]:
:: 始める
: shipment [n]:
:: 発送
: get here [v]:
:: 到着する
: distributor [n]:
:: 代理店 卸売業者
: make up for [v]:
:: 埋め合わせをする
:: to make a bad situation seem better, by providing something nice
: apology [n]:
:: 謝罪
: spill [v]:
:: こぼす


! Phrase

!! Apologies
* I apologize for ...
* I'm really sorry (for|that) ...
* I'm sorry (for|that) ...
* Sorry  (for|that) ...

* My apologies for ...
* I would like to offer my apologies for ...

!! Avoidance

* It won't happen again.
* From now on, we will always...
* I can assure you, in the future we will...
